://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Boulter\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 449}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's singles\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 507}, {\"ngram\": \"an 'unfair advantage\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's absolutely nothing to do with tennis, it's instead to do with a quirky new hobby the British players have picked up in the French capital.\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 687, \"end\": 694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9958793669220517, \"rank\": 0.003914584434100859, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 725, \"end\": 731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6939282287945415, \"rank\": 0.4257054109622632, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 620}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 638}, {\"ngram\": \"a quirky new hobby\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boulter was quizzed about what it was like having Murray on the Team GB team and toldHeart Radio: 'I mean, he is probably the pro in pin collecting, he takes it very seriously.\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 792, \"end\": 798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0214065484664943e-22, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Boulter\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"the Team GB team\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"toldHeart Radio\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"the pro\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Ever since the accreditation line that we were picking up our badges, he was right on the ball and getting as many as he could.\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 1048, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the accreditation line\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"our badges\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 989}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, he does a slight, unfair advantage because a lot of people come up to him for selfies and he's trading that for pins, which is interesting.\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a slight, unfair advantage\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1101}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"selfies\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"pins\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1169}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You know, tough to keep up!\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We all get given pins from our countries, and every other country has their own pin as well.\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1315, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pins\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"our countries\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"every other country\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"their own pin\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some have a few pins which are unique, and some are special, and some are not, but they trade them.\", \"from\": 1316, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few pins\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1336}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'So, at night you will see people go out - we went out last night, like all of us together on our Team GB bikes - looking for pins and some people that we can trade pins with.\", \"from\": 1417, \"to\": 1592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1515, \"end\": 1522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9980213669478941, \"rank\": 0.001982292162308306, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1430}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1450}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1498}, {\"ngram\": \"pins\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"some people\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"pins\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's insane, it is.\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1614, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's very unique and very special, but some are better than others, I will say that.\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1699, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not sure my game's there yet!'\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my game\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murraypaid an emotional farewellto Wimbledon this year and one of his sponsors, Castore, has urged those in SW19 to rename Church Road as 'Murray Mile' in his honour.\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an emotional farewellto Wimbledon\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1781}, {\"ngram\": \"his sponsors\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"SW19\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1849}, {\"ngram\": \"Church Road\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"'Murray Mile\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1887}, {\"ngram\": \"his honour\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Andy's legacy is unequalled,' Tom Beahon, Castore co-founder said.\", \"from\": 1905, \"to